Dialogue: 69,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:35.73,0:00:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin...
Dialogue: 69,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shot by a sniper rifle from outside...
Dialogue: 69,0:00:42.94,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They got Nezu!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sense any Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:49.52,0:00:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet that killed you wasn't from a Shadow copy,\Nit was from a real rifle.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Having Nezu so far was a mistake!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:59.36,0:01:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If only he'd been close enough for ya to sense the Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:04.47,0:01:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up bad!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew Nezu would be keeping watch as a sniper.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:10.83,0:01:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she'd come directly after me again!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, ain't their goal to keep ya alive, Shin?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing ya just restarts the loop, so why?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:28.07,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine realized that we're looping together.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:35.31,0:01:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The loop start point moves up each time.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:39.76,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell that the deadline's getting close.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:44.49,0:01:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The edges of time
Dialogue: 69,0:01:46.93,0:01:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are slowly but surely crumbling away.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:52.42,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get killed at the same point in time again, then I'll probably
Dialogue: 69,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,only have one loop left.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:00.02,0:02:00.20,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:19.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's come to the point where I just want to hoard all your words
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:25.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Even the ramblings from your travels are treasures to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:28.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Whether I sketch or erase it's all torn away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:32.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That's the price I pay for my awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:37.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or my daydream's tricking me and I'm still lost in the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Illuminated by the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Your figure casts a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}And when that silhouette wavers slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That happens to be my cue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:56.86,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I wish this were fiction but slow motion is how it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:03:02.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}If the visceral warmth and traces you left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:08.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Are protecting someone's future, I'll play the warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Amidst pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I'll conquer my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's a paradox of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or perhaps God's algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}When our tactics overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:29.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}We'll be laughing
