Dialogue: 69,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say this is the "limit."
Dialogue: 69,0:03:41.43,0:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I die, I return to this marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:55.67,signs - hr,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1192,404)\fscx81\fscy81\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&HF5F5F6&\blur1\fad(1024,0)}Limit
