Dialogue: 69,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back further than the limit,\Nso this is the starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:53.30,signs - hr,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554,405)\fscx81\fscy81\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&HF8F9FB&\blur1\fad(687,0)}Death
Dialogue: 69,0:03:49.89,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last loop, I died at 7:55 PM.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And this loop began at 6:40 PM.
