Dialogue: 69,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Time moves on from this point.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:58.17,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine I'm walking forward at a set speed until the current time, 7:20 PM.
