Dialogue: 69,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The limit also moves forward.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:06.58,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been slower than my walking pace so far,\Nso it hasn't caught up.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But every time I die, it speeds up.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:14.03,0:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya die again, where will the next start point be?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:18.67,0:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd guess...
Dialogue: 69,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,just after 7 PM.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I'm killed at the same point as last time,
Dialogue: 69,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or maybe even earlier,
Dialogue: 69,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there won't be a ninth loop.
