Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:39.93,signs - hr,,0,0,0,,{\pos(303,72)\fscx61\fscy61\fax0.11\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&HE9E8F3&\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5}Death
