Dialogue: 69,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the limit will move ahead of me.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you go back, there's no place to land.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll fall down into the darkness below the cliff.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, is that really true?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this all just yer assumptions?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's seen it as the observer.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:02.20,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That cliff is the limit of your observation.\NThe "event horizon."
Dialogue: 69,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fall, your death will be permanent.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:08.33,0:05:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The world that follows will be as Haine has foreseen it.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine must've realized that, which is why she's trying to kill Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she find me?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:21.21,0:05:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine found out about the plan in the fourth loop.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was likely when she scanned me.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:27.77,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I took lethal damage in the last scene of the fourth loop.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:32.16,0:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably fought before then and my memories were read.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:37.57,0:05:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How do Shadows share information amongst themselves?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they show memories like ya do?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They also talk and share physical notes with each other.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But Haine can also use telepathy.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:49.04,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can probably assume that the Shadows in contact with her have experienced pseudo-loops just like us.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait a second.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't ya say data can be saved through loops?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:59.36,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then ain't it possible they copied my rifle?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If they did, this place ain't safe.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:08.53,0:06:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When a print of a copied item gets too far from the Shadow, it naturally disappears.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:13.25,0:06:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Copies can only exist within 50 meters of a Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:18.13,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, basically, even if they copied a long-ranged rifle,\Nthe bullet couldn't fly more than 50 meters.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:25.87,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with unlimited bullets, that's pointless.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:29.12,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy got the better of me last time,\Nbut I also learned something.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine knows my location thanks to this brand.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:37.27,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She will definitely come here to witness my death.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We settle this tonight.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:00.93,0:07:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming at ya head-on.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya sure brought an army, Shide.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:15.77,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you seem to have gained allies as well, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the others.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they hiding?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a trap?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like y'all.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't stoop to cowardly measures.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:32.81,0:07:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just drop the petty tricks and fight fair and square.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:37.27,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You seem quite confident.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds just fine.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer too cool!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:03.45,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my life they're after, so I'll be the bait.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for fighting fair and square!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are ya taking Shin?!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajiro Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand him.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:20.06,0:08:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That Shadow called Shide—it really has no weakness.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it invincible?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa 'n' the rest of y'all, come with me.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll go after Shinpei and Ushio.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mio, go and finish off that hunter.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:02.26,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, Mother.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this area to me.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you'll be able to hear this,
Dialogue: 69,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's something important I forgot to tell you, Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:36.46,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here! Yer turn, kids!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shadow!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take ya down!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 69,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya idiot.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya oughta fix that bad habit of getting heated and charging off ahead.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosencrantz.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Guildenstern.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go wild.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Be as quiet as an explosion.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi... zu... ru...
Dialogue: 69,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asa!
Dialogue: 69,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dodge to the left.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:42.34,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I foresaw that shot hitting!
Dialogue: 69,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya she'd cover for him.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 69,0:11:01.95,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuu!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has the sight!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:05.45,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She can see my movements two seconds into the future!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, {\i1}blam{\i0}!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nezu!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With no scope?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:27.36,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That elder gentleman is quite the marksman.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya okay, Shide?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep out of his line of sight.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite dangerous.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:43.08,0:11:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, Mio, what's taking ya so long?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokiko?!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:53.57,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Guil, crush that thing.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Halt!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokiko is not yer master.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Tokiko.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill her!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Haine?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:26.21,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That stray's connection with me has been severed.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who could do this
Dialogue: 69,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is Ushio.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:36.50,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya mad? Try and reach me!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:48.40,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, this is going to be very fun.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:19.54,0:13:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yer body's so graceful.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mio is athletic, after all.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could watch this forever.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a shame.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:55.23,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for fighting "fair and square," eh?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You meanie-heads. \NI believed you for a second, too.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pure-hearted, I'll have you know.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:06.71,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew y'all would chase me.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:08.79,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if ya knew it was a trap.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like ya have the upper hand the whole time, just like ya are now.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Think yer above us, do ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Shinpei's above even y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.94,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.94,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 69,0:14:39.98,0:14:40.25,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 69,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That gas created a sea of fire.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadows have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's working!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:54.34,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shadows are weak to fire, just like I thought!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Papa, Mama.\NIt's hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kill him, it'll fix everything!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come 'n' get some!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By looking down on us,
Dialogue: 69,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,ya took yer eyes off the prize, Haine.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's for Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:48.56,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll erase ya!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:54.08,0:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are ya planning on grinning stupidly with Shiori's face, ya fake?!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:03.86,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop... Don't erase me!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:09.43,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided this would be the body.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:12.85,0:16:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna return with this girl and her family.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be together forever.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:20.07,0:16:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be fooled by yer crocodile tears!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 69,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}don't erase me!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:33.31,0:16:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's still alive!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:52.97,0:16:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You cannot kill me with fire, b-b-b-but...
Dialogue: 69,0:16:57.25,0:17:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it can, can, can kill y-y-you!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I realized some-something.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:03.91,0:17:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You, you and Haine can b-bring the information you hold into the next loop.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:09.37,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In, in other words, if your data is harmed or kill, kill, killed...
Dialogue: 69,0:17:13.45,0:17:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that gets brought into the next the next{not a typo} loop, correct?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:18.04,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take Shinpei a few minutes, minutes to die.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed his vitals on purpose, you see.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:26.55,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when you die—die before, before him?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:32.98,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm so curious, -urious to find, to find out!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 69,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not interested in finding out.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't fixin' to die just yet!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so fast...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:14.01,0:18:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't e-e-even realize you'd swapped places.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:17.35,0:18:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the, the, the thing I'd grabbed on to
Dialogue: 69,0:18:20.29,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was a clump of hair with your dummy printed on it...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer not invincible.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll erase ya!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:38.25,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A person's hand?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's someone inside!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames are gone?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 69,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,did...
Dialogue: 69,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She got away.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:35.41,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close to erasing her.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shide, ya okay?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can return after some restructuring.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How are Mommy and Daddy?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei was mortally wounded.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:58.91,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll die in a few minutes,\N and the final loop will begin.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:26.90,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just tired from copying so much.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But yer bleeding!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya ever fake that yer fine in front of me!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei...
Dialogue: 69,0:20:38.48,0:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This blood's because some glass hit my projected body.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:41.99,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But weren't ya shot?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A bulletproof vest.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw how to make one online.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoulder and side were hit too!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:20.68,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames caused by the gasoline and match were essentially data.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:25.45,0:21:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They only burned what she wanted them to, \Nmeaning we and the building were unaffected.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Flames were effective against the Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The normal Shadows that have fused with Shide died instantly,
Dialogue: 69,0:21:36.62,0:21:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and even Shide was slowed by them.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:40.17,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Ushio's hacking coincidentally revealed a human body within Shide.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Haine scanned and erased the air in the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:50.98,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The resulting vacuum inside the building caused the outside air to instantly rush in,
Dialogue: 69,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing them to escape.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:57.37,0:22:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All before we could scan Shide's true form.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:01.54,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the air? How?
Dialogue: 69,0:22:04.49,0:22:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can copy air and liquids too.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:07.68,0:22:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it needs some kind of container.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:11.28,0:22:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio was able to scan the gasoline inside a can, after all.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:15.21,0:22:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible if you think of the gymnasium as the vessel.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, even though she's our enemy.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:22.34,0:22:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have that kind of power to scan something on such a large scale.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:27.64,0:22:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating!
Dialogue: 69,0:22:30.48,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, tonight was a fruitful night.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:32.83,0:22:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone survived.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what matters most.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:41.13,0:22:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:42.72,0:22:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:44.20,0:22:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mere.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:46.36,0:22:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it go as planned?
Dialogue: 69,0:22:47.64,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:49.53,0:22:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme ask ya one more time, Ushio.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Once ya cut that connection, that link with Haine,
Dialogue: 69,0:22:55.48,0:22:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is it really, truly safe?
Dialogue: 69,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked well with Ros and Guil.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:01.05,0:23:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:01.83,0:23:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just mess with their heads a little.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:04.40,0:23:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, I just have to make them the same as me.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:07.52,0:23:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I could easily finish it off right now.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:10.91,0:23:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya sure about this, Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:23:12.71,0:23:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:14.23,0:23:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Sis.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:19.78,0:23:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Make my Shadow one of us.
